code: import axios from"axios";export async function uploadFile(chatId,file){const formData=new FormData();formData.append('chat_id',chatId);formData.append('file',file);const res=await axios.post(`https://giicoo.ru/api/file-service/uploadfile/`,formData,{headers:{'Content-Type':'multipart/form-data'}});return res.data;}
